User shall be able to access the menu and change difficulty into an option of easy, medium, or hard (NF 13.0). 
User shall also be able to choose the music inside the menu out of a preset selection of music files (FR 1.1). 
Lastly, the user shall be able to choose a legacy version inside the menu, which includes the original soundtrack, Korobeniki and normal game functionality (FR 1.2).
